Brazil Oo Ay Gilgileen Banaan-Baxyo
Lagaga Soo Horjeedo Madaxweyne
Bolsonaro. On Jun 29, 2020 136
Addis Ababa june 29,2020 (Senee
Dibadbaxayaal ka socdadalka Brazil iyo daafaha adduunka ayaa
isu soo baxay si ay u dhalleeceeyaan
madaxweyne Jair Bolsonaro wax ka
